The categories of tense and mood and different types of complex sentences are examined during the course.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To give an overview of the main rules of French verbal categories and of the principles of syntactical analysis.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student: 1) has the knowledge of the French grammatical rules related to the categories of tense and mood and the formation of complex sentences; 2) is able to apply acquired grammatical rules in practical grammar exercises; 3) has the knowledge of the basic tools of the analysis of complex sentences; 4) can carry out an elementary syntactic analysis of French.
